ActCanadian Navigable Waters Act
SubjectOrder Exempting Certain Navigable Waters Located in Quebec from the Application of Section 23 of the Canadian Navigable Waters Act
PrecisOrder EXEMPTING CERTAIN NAVIGABLE WATERS LOCATED IN QUEBEC FROM THE APPLICATION OF SECTION 23 OF THE CANADIAN NAVIGABLE WATERS ACT in order to permit dewatering in twenty-eight (28) navigable waters, reducing water levels and facilitating mining operations.
